titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (GLUTARIC ACIDURIA TYPE 1) - Description

div.p: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (GLUTARIC ACIDURIA TYPE 1) is the same as attribute NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS.
NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (GLUTARIC ACIDURIA TYPE 1) is the result of screening for Glutarid Aciduria Type (GA1).
